summary: Puts a pair of college boots on the corpse in the Torture Room in Helgen.
descriptionHtml:
This has annoyed the sh!t out of me for ages ;)

Just adds a pair of matching college boots to the corpse in the Helgen Torture Room.

It is ages until you will find a pair of matching boots for the robe, why they weren\'t included already is beyond me.

Here they are.

(And I\'ll take that other stuff too, thanks).

[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/35175-1-1366781865.jpg[/img][/center]
author: thefinn
